A family in Nakuru county is mourning the loss of their three children who were killed by a motorist who lost control of his vehicle and ran over them before disappearing. Two of the children had accompanied their 15-year-old brother to seek advice from his father ahead of his initiation ceremony when the vehicle veered off the road and hit them And in another incident, a student died after drowning in a hotel swimming pool in Baringo county after a pool party turned tragic.  